    "en": {
      "title": "Catches 3 with 90 lakh gold and a valampuri",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy says that three suspects who tried to illegally take 470 grams of gold worth more than 90 lakh rupees and a Valampuri to India in a dinghy were arrested by the Navy in the Pesale area of \u200b\u200bMannar.",
        "The gold was arrested along with the suspects during the inspection of a suspicious dinghy yesterday night (25) during the Soci operations carried out by the Navy in the Kurupadu area of \u200b\u200bPaesali."
      ],
